            "name": "Force Dart",
            "subtype": "ability",
            "text": "The witchwyrd fires one dart of force per action spent (dealing 1d4+1 force damage each). They can't spend more actions on this ability than they have free hands. If they use a hand that has Absorbed Force, that hand hurls two darts instead of one, expending the held energy.",
